headline: BIO-TECHNE ANNOUNCES NEW DISTRIBUTION AGREEMENT WITH MEDSANTEK TO EXPAND ACCESS TO PORTFOLIO ACROSS TURKEY
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH), a global life sciences company providing innovative tools and bioactive reagents for the research and clinical diagnostic communities today announced a partnership with MedSanTek. Under the agreement, MedSanTek becomes the distributor of Bio-Techne's R&D Systems, Novus, Tocris, Protein Simple, Advanced Cell Diagnostics (ACD), and Asuragen brands across Turkey.
